These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, lily, azalea
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, trance
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who growslily##1
5. the fan of trance is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Flower         | lily | begonia   | azalea   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | blues    | folk      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, gospel, soul
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, chaman, cain
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the cain-smoker##1
4. the person eating kale is the chaman-smoker##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the fan of gospel and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | soul     | blues      |
| Cigar   | cain  | chaman | oliveros |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, paramedic
City: hannover, nizza, new-york
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the bartender is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the paramedic and the person traveling to new-york##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating kale##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Job           | paramedic | bartender  | doctor   |
| City   | hannover  | nizza    | new-york |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

