.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, cucumber, raspberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
House: townhouse, wooden, colonial
1. the townhouse house is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the paramedic and the owner of the cat##2
4. the person eating cucumber is the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | cherry       | raspberry  | cucumber   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| House   | colonial | townhouse     | wooden      |

