.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, peach, radish
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, rock, jazz
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, western
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the fan of rock is between the person eating radish and the person driving the car##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person eating peach##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the fan of rock is between the fan of jazz and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | radish      | peach   | artichoke |
| Music-Genre         | punk | rock | jazz |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | western | fantasy   |
| Transport     | van         | roller  | car       |

