.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, sunflower, tulip
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rabbit
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, surfing
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person driving the car##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person driving the car##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who growstulip##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the person driving the tram and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Flower        | sunflower      | poppy | tulip |
| Pet         | goldfish     | rabbit    | dog        |
| Sport       | snowboarding | surfing   | lacrosse   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 